Name: NivelFederacao
Title: Nível da Federação
Descriptino: Tipo de federação suportada para um PractitionerRole

Name: EventSummaryType
Title: EventSummaryType
Descriptino: Tipos de estruturas usadas para construir um registro eletrônico de saúde do tipo "sumário de evento ou contato assistencial"

Name: ServiceRequestCategory
Title: ServiceRequestCategory
Descriptino: Categorias utilizadas nos perfis do recurso ServiceRequest

Name: AdministrativeGender
Title: AdministrativeGender
Descriptino: The gender of a person used for administrative purposes.

Name: SNOMED_CT
Title: SNOMED CT (all versions)
Descriptino: SNOMED CT is the most comprehensive and precise clinical health terminology product in the world, owned and distributed around the world by The International Health Terminology Standards Development Organisation (IHTSDO).

Name: IdentifierType
Title: identifierType
Descriptino: HL7-defined code system of concepts specifying type of identifier. Used in HL7 Version 2.x messaging data types CX, PLN, PPN, XCN and XON.

Name: SpecimenType
Title: specimenType
Descriptino: HL7-defined code system of concepts that describe the precise nature of an entity that may be used as the source material for an observation.  This is one of two code systems that are used instead of table 0070 (code system 2.16.840.1.113883.18.28) which conflated specimen types and specimen collection methods.   Used in HL7 Version 2.x messaging in the SPM segment.

Name: SpecimenCondition
Title: specimenCondition
Descriptino: Code system of concepts specifying a mode or state of being that describes the nature of the specimen.  Used in HL7 Version 2.x messaging in the SPM segment.

Name: RelevantClincialInformation
Title: relevantClincialInformation
Descriptino: Code system of concepts specifying additional clinical information about the patient or specimen to report the supporting and/or suspected diagnosis and clinical findings on requests for interpreted diagnostic studies. Used in HL7 Version 2.x messaging in the OBR segment.

Name: ObservationType
Title: observationType
Descriptino: HL7-defined code system of concepts specifying types of observations to enable systems to distinguish between observations sent along with an order, versus observations sent as the result to an order. Used in HL7 Version 2.x messaging in the OBX segment.

Name: ActReason
Title: ActReason
Descriptino: A set of codes specifying the motivation, cause, or rationale of an Act, when such rationale is not reasonably represented as an ActRelationship of type "has reason" linking to another Act.    *Examples:* Example reasons that might qualify for being coded in this field might be: "routine requirement", "infectious disease reporting requirement", "on patient request", "required by law".

Name: SubstanceAdminSubstitution
Title: Substance Admin Substitution
Descriptino: Identifies what sort of change is permitted or has occurred between the therapy that was ordered and the therapy that was/will be provided.

Name: BRDivisaoGeograficaBrasil
Title: Divisão Geográfica do Brasil
Descriptino: As regiões geográficas, estados, distrito federal e municípios do Brasil.
